39
00:03:58,186 --> 00:03:59,186
Okay.

40
00:04:03,986 --> 00:04:05,686
Miwako. Did I keep you waiting?

41
00:04:05,686 --> 00:04:06,686
I'm sorry.

42
00:04:06,686 --> 00:04:08,286
I sure did.

43
00:04:08,286 --> 00:04:10,886
I mean, it's your treat today, okay?

44
00:04:10,886 --> 00:04:13,786
What? I mean, I always treat you, don't I?

45
00:04:13,786 --> 00:04:15,686
Did you say something just now?

46
00:04:15,686 --> 00:04:17,486
No, I didn't.

47
00:04:18,886 --> 00:04:21,886
So shall we get going, then?

48
00:04:21,886 --> 00:04:22,886
I guess so.

49
00:04:31,786 --> 00:04:34,486
Put the money in this briefcase.

50
