54
00:04:44,186 --> 00:04:46,886
Dispose of the microphone you're using to keep in touch with the police.

55
00:04:49,086 --> 00:04:52,886
M is headed again north on Chuo Boulevard.

56
00:04:52,886 --> 00:04:53,886
Roger.

57
00:04:56,486 --> 00:04:57,486
Conan.

58
