66
00:05:21,086 --> 00:05:23,886
Well, I'm sorry to have kept you waiting.

67
00:05:26,486 --> 00:05:28,186
Are you Mr. Ishida?

68
00:05:28,186 --> 00:05:29,386
Yes.

69
00:05:29,386 --> 00:05:31,386
We thought you weren't going to come anymore.

70
00:05:31,386 --> 00:05:32,886
I'm so sorry.

71
00:05:35,386 --> 00:05:38,886
I'm sorry everyone, for making you wait.

72
00:05:38,886 --> 00:05:41,186
Okay, since everyone's on board,

73
00:05:41,186 --> 00:05:42,886
we'll start off.

74
00:05:51,386 --> 00:05:53,486
The cruiser that M is on board has departed.

75
00:05:56,486 --> 00:05:57,986
Sir.

