That's going to Sumida River then to Ooyoko River.

79
00:06:07,186 --> 00:06:09,186
Would you like a pamphlet?

80
00:06:09,186 --> 00:06:10,786
Thank you.

81
00:06:10,786 --> 00:06:12,986
"Spring Cherry Blossom Viewing Cruise"

82
00:06:15,886 --> 00:06:17,786
But, inspector...

83
00:06:17,786 --> 00:06:21,386
Why did the culprit designate me to bring him the money?

84
00:06:21,386 --> 00:06:23,786
The thing is, I don't really know.

85
00:06:23,786 --> 00:06:26,386
Don't you have any idea why?

