92
00:06:41,986 --> 00:06:44,686
I can't afford to endanger the lives of my employees.

93
00:06:44,686 --> 00:06:46,186
I understand.

94
00:06:46,186 --> 00:06:49,286
You can count on me, Kogoro Mouri.

95
00:06:55,686 --> 00:06:58,886
We will be entering Sumida River in about 10 minutes,

96
